name: Design Master Doors
tag_list: exterior-doors, entry-doors, interior-doors, french-doors, glass-doors, wood-doors, krosswood-doors
overview: DesignMasterDoors.com founded in 2010 provides premium quality exterior and interior doors direct to customers without middlemen. By keeping overhead low through internet marketing, DesignMasterDoors.com can offer beautiful imported and custom made exterior doors, entry doors and interior doors at low prices. DesignMasterDoors.com is an authorized internet retailer of Krosswood Doors - a leader in knotty alder wood door imports. With over six years experience in finish carpentry and custom door products in Utah, the owners can design and offer complete packages including sidelights, transoms, trim and moldings.
